<view class="page paper-page diary-page theme-diary">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box diary-head title-pattern-card"><image class="title-pattern-image" src="/assets/tabbar-source/dark-green.png" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="title-pattern-mask"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--green"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <text class="eyebrow">本地日记记录</text>
    <text class="hero-title">吗喽的日记本</text>
    <text class="subtext">先写下来，再慢慢看清。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="ornament-card dashboard-summary-card status-card {{dashboardSummary.statusClass}} croissant-status-card">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--green"></view>
    <view class="croissant-status-header">
      <text class="amulet-frame__seal croissant-status-label">Croissant 最近状态</text>
      <text class="status-name croissant-status-name">{{dashboardSummary.status}}</text>
      <text class="status-wear croissant-wear-chip">磨损值：{{dashboardSummary.wear}}</text>
    </view>
    <text class="body-text croissant-status-text summary-text">{{dashboardSummary.text}}</text>
    <view class="amulet-note croissant-advice-panel"><text class="protect-label">保护建议</text><text>{{dashboardSummary.advice}}</text></view>
    <view class="summary-meta croissant-status-stats">
      <text>最近共记录 {{dashboardSummary.total}} 条</text>
      <text>近 7 天高影响事件 {{dashboardSummary.highImpact7Days}} 条</text>
    </view>
    <view class="summary-actions croissant-status-actions">
      <button class="sticker-button secondary summary-button" bindtap="goDashboard">查看决心仪表盘</button>
      <button class="sticker-button secondary summary-button" bindtap="goNew">写一条日记</button>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="filter-panel archive-filter"><view wx:for="{{typeFilters}}" wx:key="key" class="chip {{activeFilter === item.key ? 'pink' : ''}}" data-key="{{item.key}}" bindtap="switchTypeFilter">{{item.label}}</view></view>
  <scroll-view class="reason-scroll" scroll-x="true"><view class="reason-row-filter"><view wx:for="{{reasonFilters}}" wx:key="*this" class="chip {{(activeReason === 'all' && item === '全部归因') || activeReason === item ? 'green' : ''}}" data-reason="{{item}}" bindtap="switchReasonFilter">{{item}}</view></view></scroll-view>

  <view wx:if="{{!entries.length}}" class="empty-card diary-empty">
    <view class="paper-divider"><view class="paper-divider__line"></view><text class="paper-divider__tag">空白纸页</text><view class="paper-divider__line"></view></view>
    <text>这里暂时没有符合筛选的记录。</text>
    <text>第一条记录不需要完美，只要真实。</text>
    <text>你不是在小题大做，你是在替自己留下线索。</text>
  </view>

  <view wx:for="{{entries}}" wx:key="id" class="archive-card memo-paper entry-card {{item.cardClass}} paper-edge {{item.impactLevel >= 4 ? 'red-mark' : ''}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="goDetail">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--blue"></view>
    <view class="paper-corner bottom-right"></view>
    <view class="entry-topline">
      <text class="date">{{item.displayDate}}</text>
      <text class="paper-seal entry-type negative">{{item.typeLabel}}</text>
    </view>
    <text class="summary">{{item.summary}}</text>
    <view class="entry-meta-grid">
      <view class="entry-meta-item"><text class="meta-label">影响</text><text class="meta-value {{item.impactClass}}">{{item.impactLevel}} 级</text></view>
      <view class="entry-meta-item"><text class="meta-label">归因</text><text class="meta-value">{{item.primaryReason}}</text></view>
    </view>
    <view class="memo-slip"><text class="memo-label">事实纪要摘录</text><text class="memo">{{item.memoPreview}}</text></view>
    <text class="detail-hint">点开查看完整记录</text>
  </view>
</view>
